Game : Vigilante 8 2nd Offense
Date : 2003.09.03
Video: PAL
Ripped by: DCP
Rip notes: nothing

This gut-searing Sega Dreamcast title will get you revved up with non-stop on- and off-road driving combined with machine-gunning auto-combat action. Choose from 15 different vehicles, each with its own driving abilities and weapons. Thrash your opponents with special attack moves and new power-ups in fully destructible battle arenas. Increase vehicle attributes as you play, and earn points towards the ultimate vehicle upgrade that you can save and play against your cohorts. Various modes provide a slew of single, two-player, and four-player options. 
Get ready for the heaviest metal and rubber-burning brawl of the century!